Installation instructions:

Install composer, npm. Fork this code.
Install silex with command:
    composer install silex/silex
Install angularjs in /web directory with command:
    npm install angularjs

Next install mysql or another DB that PHP:PDO(more info: http://php.net/manual/ru/book.pdo.php) can connect.
    resource sqldump in tt.sql file

Don't forget to edit DB connector configuration in api/config.php